     SHORT="Bigloo is an implementation of the Scheme programming language"
cat << EOF
An implementation of the Scheme programming language. 
It relies on an optimizing compiler from Scheme to C. 
Bigloo enables connections between Scheme code and C code. I
t proposes many extensions to Scheme such as a regular parser 
compiler, an lalr parser compiler, pattern matching, an object layer, etc.
EOF
